OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying very warm or hot Thursday,
OL,7,Fthough perhaps cooler along cloudier
OL,8,Fcoasts. Hot again Friday with long
OL,9,Fsunny periods, though thundery showers
OL,10,Fmay develop. Perhaps turning cooler
OL,11,Fwith showers Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
